  "description": "Hapax / Audio / Recovery Events. xHCI controller recovery events, BT firmware reload events, and broadcast-master integrated LUFS gauge. Sources: scripts/hapax-xhci-death-watchdog + scripts/hapax-bt-firmware-watchdog (textfile collector under /var/lib/node_exporter/textfile_collector/) and shared/broadcast_audio_health.py per-tick LUFS measurement. Cc-task: audio-audit-H3-prometheus-recovery-counters.",
